Company Profile

Operations
Production of total vacuum equipment and components for quartz devices, optical thin films, 
electronic devices, etc.
          : Vacuum evaporation equipment / Sputtering equipment / lon plating 
          equipment / Dry etching, ashing equipment / Vacuum metallurgic equipment 
          (for dissolution, heat-processing, sintering and degassing) / Optical 
          monitor for thin films (multi-color, monochrome) / IAD cold cathode 
          ion source / Liquid crystal injection equipment / etc.


Foundation
September 1953


Incorporation
August 1958


Capital
¥2.17 billion (March 2017)

Management


President (Officer)Kunimasa Omata
Director (Officer)Tadashi Ichikawa
Director (Officer)Osamu Takahashi
Director (Officer)Hiromi Kushima
Director (Officer)Shoichi Tanaka
Director 
Masasuke Matsudai  (President of ULVAC TECHNO, 
                Ltd.)

AuditorYoshinosuke Muraki
AuditorEiichi Chiba (Lawyer)
Auditor
Seiichi Takahashi (Auditor of ULVAC, Inc.)


Banks
Bank of Tokyo-Mitsubishi UFJ Bank of Yokohama MIZUHO Bank Sumitomo Mitsui 
BankYachiyo BankYamanashi Chuo Bank Jonan Credit Bank

Number of Employees
180 (March 2017) 

Research and Development Equipment
Multilayer evaporation equipment 
for optical components / Etching frequency adjustment equipment / Inter-back sputtering 
equipment / Carrousel sputtering equipment / Plasma CVD / GCIB fine processing 
equipment / Roll-to-roll small sputtering equipment / Other sputtering equipment 
/ Electronic microscope / Contact probe profilometer / Ellipsometer / Spectrophotometer 
/ etc. 

Major Customers 
 KYOCERA Corporation / Seiko Epson Corporation / DAISHINKU CORP. / 
          NIHON DEMPA KOGYO CO., LTD. / Murata Manufacturing Company, Ltd. / various 
          electronic component makers, universities and government research institutes.

Group Companies
SHOWA SHINKU MACHINERY (SHANGHAI) CO., LTD.
          SHOWA SHINKU MACHINERY TRADING (SHANGHAI) CO., LTD.
          FEC CORPORATION

Affiliated Company 
Sansei-Showa Co., Ltd. USA


