Product Information



SHOWA SHINKU manufactures and sells vacuum equipment such as Vacuum evaporation equipment, Sputtering equipment and etc. , which uses vacuum technology and mainly forms thin films on a specific substrate.

for Quartz Devices
Mobile communication devices such as SAW filters, crystal units and crystal oscillators 
 for Electronic Devices
Our advanced thin-film coating technology using a vacuum meets a variety of needs in a wide range of fields.
 for Optical Devices
Vacuum technology plays an important role in the opto-electonics sector.
 Components
Oil diffusion pump (inner heat type) and others
 New Technology
Our new technologies for the next-generation
reNew!
 Application Examples
Our equipment plays a role in manufacturing of many devices.

